            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23693068">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23693068/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p23693068-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">理想国的建立（示意图）—— 各职业的诞生： </span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23693068/">(<span class="">5回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-06 15:17</span>
                  
